Zips `self` with another `Option`.

If `self` is `Some(s)` and `other` is `Some(o)`, this method returns `Some((s, o))`.
Otherwise, `None` is returned.

# Examples

```
let x = Some(1);
let y = Some("hi");
let z = None::<u8>;

assert_eq!(x.zip(y), Some((1, "hi")));
assert_eq!(x.zip(z), None);
```
